  <title>Cherry Tomato Bake</title>
  <filename>cherry_tomato_bake.xml</filename>
  <htmlFilename>cherry_tomato_bake.html</htmlFilename>
  <comment/>
  <thumbnail>cherry_tomato_bake.jpeg</thumbnail>
  <image/>
  <category/>
  <yield/>
  <prepTime>PT0M</prepTime>
  <cookTime>PT0M</cookTime>
  <ingredient>4 cups cherry tomatos halved</ingredient>
  <ingredient>3 cloves garlic minced </ingredient>
  <ingredient>2 TBsp olive oil </ingredient>
  <ingredient>1/4 teaspoon Salt and Pepper</ingredient>
  <ingredient>1/2 cup feta crumbled</ingredient>
  <ingredient>1 bunch dill chopped</ingredient>
  <step>Preheat oven to 180C while preparing the ingredients.</step>
  <step>In shallow baking dish place all ingredients.</step>
  <step>Cook for 30-40 mins.</step>
  <step>When tomatoes have all collapsed remove from oven.</step>
  <step>Stir and sprinkle with additional dill if desired.</step>
  <step>Serve with BBQ meat.</step>
  <step>* different variety tomatos can be used, I prefer 2 red and 1 yellow punnet.</step>
</recipe>
